songs.title: You Already Know Me (Ft. Kreayshawn)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse: V-Nasty]
You already know me, lil V-Nasty
Snatchin 30 bands, and I toat that gass
V-nasty, V-Nasty
You already know that, I put you in your bag
Off 3 pills, money on my mind, and I don't wear heals
Sellin them pounds, drinkin on purp
You already know me, I'm leanin off the blow
I don't give a fuck, cause I got hella hoes
Delo, Delo
You ain't got no hoes
Sleepy, fuck it, V
